      "text": "He has a lot of regrets."
    },
    {
      "start": 405.78,
      "end": 406.34,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.36,
      "end": 408.0,
      "text": "And he's regretting about his past."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.0,
      "end": 414.18,
      "text": "자, 자신의 과거에 가졌던 그런 꿈들에 대해서 뭐라고 하는지 차차 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.18,
      "end": 418.6,
      "text": "When I was young, I passionately wanted two things."
    },
    {
      "start": 418.6,
      "end": 419.1,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.1,
      "end": 424.22,
      "text": "When I was young, 이렇게 시작을 하니까, when I was young, 이 팝송이 생각이 나네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.28,
      "end": 424.98,
      "text": "Oh, 팝송."
    },
    {
      "start": 424.98,
      "end": 429.6,
      "text": "내가 젊었을 때, I passionately wanted two things."
    },
    {
      "start": 429.86,
      "end": 430.74,
      "text": "해석하고 계시죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.2,
      "end": 434.26,
      "text": "나는 열정적으로 wanted two things."
    },
    {
      "start": 434.48,
      "end": 435.8,
      "text": "두 가지를 원했지."
    },
    {
      "start": 435.8,
      "end": 443.16,
      "text": "I think of my dad, when he was scolding us, and we would 도망가고 싶었을 때, we would want to run away."
    },
    {
      "start": 443.36,
      "end": 446.46,
      "text": "When I was your age, we used to do so many..."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.46,
      "end": 447.02,
      "text": "라트는 말이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 447.3,
      "end": 447.7,
      "text": "이거죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.8,
      "end": 448.34,
      "text": "그거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.54,
      "end": 449.82,
      "text": "약간 꼰대스러운 표현이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 450.0,
      "end": 451.86,
      "text": "아, when I was young, 꼰대스러운."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.1,
      "end": 453.82,
      "text": "Of course, it depends on the context."
    },
    {
      "start": 453.82,
      "end": 456.16,
      "text": "But I think of that."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.76,
      "end": 459.48,
      "text": "When I was young, I passionately wanted two things."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.28,
      "end": 461.54,
      "text": "I wanted to get married."
    },
    {
      "start": 461.84,
      "end": 464.18,
      "text": "Oh, so one of his dreams was to get married."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.56,
      "end": 466.26,
      "text": "And it didn't work out."
    },
    {
      "start": 466.34,
      "end": 466.9,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.24,
      "end": 470.42,
      "text": "그의 꿈 중에 하나가 결혼을 하는 것이었다고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.52,
      "end": 471.46,
      "text": "Marriage is good."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.18,
      "end": 473.72,
      "text": "근데 그걸 못 이룬 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.22,
      "end": 477.7,
      "text": "And his other dream, I wanted to become an author."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.7,
      "end": 480.18,
      "text": "Wow, I wanted to become an author."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.18,
      "end": 483.88,
      "text": "그리고 나는 작가가 되고 싶었어 라는 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.4,
      "end": 487.3,
      "text": "So he tried to encourage his nephew's dream."
    },
    {
