      "end": 488.22,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.5,
      "end": 491.24,
      "text": "Because his nephew wants to be an artist."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.32,
      "end": 491.76,
      "text": "그죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 492.12,
      "end": 495.48,
      "text": "He wants to direct his own plays and be an actor in them."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.35,
      "end": 499.83,
      "text": "I never managed either one."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.03,
      "end": 500.87,
      "text": "그런데..."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.87,
      "end": 502.43,
      "text": "He could not do either one."
    },
    {
      "start": 502.65,
      "end": 502.79,
      "text": "그죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 502.93,
      "end": 505.53,
      "text": "결혼하는 것, 그리고 작가가 되는 것, 둘 다."
    },
    {
      "start": 505.53,
      "end": 508.67,
      "text": "I never managed either one, either one."
    },
    {
      "start": 508.67,
      "end": 511.51,
      "text": "둘 중에 하나도 내가 해낸 게 없어."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.07,
      "end": 513.53,
      "text": "Yeah, either one, either one."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.59,
      "end": 514.43,
      "text": "둘 다 가능하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 514.49,
