      "text": "It's so poetic."
    },
    {
      "start": 547.96,
      "end": 548.48,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.74,
      "end": 552.1,
      "text": "Even the thought of her makes my heart race."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.66,
      "end": 554.92,
      "text": "심지어 그녀를 떠올리기만 해도"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.92,
