      "start": 623.3,
      "end": 623.68,
      "text": "혈기."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.72,
      "end": 624.24,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.44,
      "end": 625.24,
      "text": "왕성할 때."
    },
    {
      "start": 625.38,
      "end": 627.28,
      "text": "왕성한 혈기 느낄 수가 있었고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.48,
      "end": 631.08,
      "text": "Have you ever been insanely happy or insanely in love?"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.22,
      "end": 633.02,
      "text": "Oh, 그때가 언제였더라?"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.46,
      "end": 634.8,
      "text": "I don't remember."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.96,
      "end": 635.48,
      "text": "How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.44,
      "end": 638.1,
      "text": "Let's talk about it later."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.1,
      "end": 639.88,
      "text": "I'm always happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.08,
